Package com.whirvis.jraknet.server

Components used to create RakNet servers.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RakNetServerListener
    Used to listen for events that occur in the RakNetServer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlockedAddress
    An address that the server has blocked.
    RakNetServer
    Used to create servers using the RakNet protocol.
    RakNetServerHandler
    Used by the RakNetServer with the sole purpose of sending received packets to the server so they can be handled.
    ServerPing
    Contains information about a server ping such as who sent the ping and what the server will respond back with.
